Class NettyPooledTcpTransport<M extends AbstractRequest>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibasco.agql.core.transport.NettyTransport<M>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - A type of AbstractRequest that will be used as a lookup reference for our key
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Transport<M>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class NettyPooledTcpTransport<M extends AbstractRequest>
extends NettyPooledTransport<M,InetSocketAddress>

    A Pooled TCP Transport implementation which creates and reuse channels stored within a pool map. InetSocketAddress is used as the key for the ChannelPoolMap implementation
